# Aspire Leadership Program | Master Repository

This repository serves as the centralized development and documentation hub for the final core blocks of the Aspire Leadership Program: **Week 7 (Communicating for Impact)** and **Week 8 (Leading in Professional Spaces)**. It houses all case study solutions, architectural stakeholder mapping models, technical personal statements, and program reflections.

